Class TerminalSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nineml.coffeegrinder.parser.Symbol
      • org.nineml.coffeegrinder.parser.TerminalSymbol

  • public class TerminalSymbol
extends Symbol
    A terminal symbol.

    Terminal symbols match some input token(s) literally.
